data.description: *** POOL HOME WITH OUTDOOR KITCHEN ***NEW ROOF 2023 *** NEW A/C 2022 *** NEW WATER HEATER 2022 ** STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES INCLUDED *** POOL HOME WITH OUTDOOR KITCHEN *** FULLY FENCED IN BACK YARD *** LOW MAINTENANCE BACK YARD WITH ARTIFICIAL TURF ***.   Step into elegance in this stunning 4 bedroom, 3 bath, two-story home  located in the beautifully mature community of Cypress Creek. Come home from a long day of work to a gorgeous, modern and fabulous dry bar to pour a cocktail, mocktail or a glass of wine. Enter your newly renovated and updated kitchen for a social hour or entertaining while making your favorite meals on your brand new appliances. If you're feeling a bit sluggish you can always pour a cup of coffee from your built-in coffee bar that is also the home to your very own customized built-in cabinets. Open up the french doors leading out to the glistening pool, and fenced in the backyard. No need to waste water on your green grass, this backyard is perfectly paved and done right with astro turf. Show off your grill skills with your very own outdoor kitchen including a grill top, side burners, mini fridge and kegerator for a night with friends or hosting your own pool party!!  .Upstairs you will be tucked away with your large bonus room and the oversized master bedroom, walk-in closet, master bath, large laundry room, two guest bedrooms and a guest bath. . HOA fees are low at $229 quarterly and includes Spectrum cable & internet, and trash collection. Be the envy of all your friends with this fabulous find!! This home is vacant and move in ready!!!
